Program: Outlook
Title: Shashi Tharoor
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs84
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
An interview with the possible new UN new secretary general, Indian writer Shashi Tharoor. Also, part three of Thembi Ngubane's audio diary on living with HIV in South Africa. Mike Thexton and air crew members on surviving a 16 hour aeroplane hijack in Pakistan in 1986 which ended with 20 passengers dead. Finally, Dr Diablo on debt collecting in Venezula. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less